node.title: Body found in North Shore's Lake Pupuke
node.description: The man was reportedly swimming with a friend on Tuesday night and got into trouble.
node.content:
["A man's body has been found in Lake Pupuke on Auckland's North Shore.", "", "
Lake Pupuke, Takapuna, Auckland. Photo: 123RF
", "The man was reportedly swimming with a friend on Tuesday night and got into trouble.", "The Police National Dive Squad recovered the man's body last night."]
